@rem -------------------------------------------------------
@node "WhatIsThis" "What is this ?"

@{b}         Artificial Intelligence manual@{ub}
Documentation version 1.1 written on 16 September 2000

Welcome to the manual for amiga's artificial intelligence simulator.
We are very pleased that you've downloaded this archive and would like
to ask you kindly to inform HellHound about your experiences playing
with the simulator. This will help advancing a better and newer simulator.
@{"Contact HellHound" link HellCoder}

@{b}Artificial intelligence@{ub}
Have you ever been interested in artificial intelligence but never had the
opportunity to experience with it ?, this program will quide you through
all basic knowledge which will give you a better understanding of the concept.
If you haven't got the time you shouldn't bother running a simulation because
you won't be amused at all. This program will only be fun if you're actually
interested in the subject.

My advice is to carefully read all documentation before starting a simulation.
@endnode
@rem -------------------------------------------------------

